This project showcases a professional UX/UI design for our innovative smart refrigerator, Smart Frost. The refrigerator is supported by an external device that displays intuitive interfaces and smart features aimed at improving food management and user convenience.

Key features include:

Connect your mobile device and browse smart fridge interfaces.

Automatic scanning and logging of any item placed in the fridge, including item name and expiration date.

Generate a smart shopping list based on current items.

Directly order items from partnered supermarkets.

Receive notifications when quantities are low or items are about to expire.

View nutritional values of stored foods.

Get guidance on proper storage methods and ideal placement within the fridge.

Discover recipe suggestions based on available ingredients.

This project focuses on blending technology, user-centered design, and practical everyday functionality to enhance the future of food storage.

